SubjectRegulations Amending the Fish Inspection Regulations
PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE FISH INSPECTION REGULATIONS in order to provide greater flexibility to industry to use any product that is safe and available to them on the market without having to wait for the product to go through the process to be included on the Reference Listing.
